        span Style Ed-at-Large NYLON Mag
      .content
        h2.blogger-title.quote I'm inspired by my environment, travel, creativity is everywhere.
        .interview
          .title Our Interview with Dani
          .q How would you describe your personal style?
          .a Fun. Eclectic. 

          .q Whatâ€™s one piece of fashion advice you could give to a girl preparing to go to her formal?
          .a Make sure the dress is flattering on your figure. Don't wear something just because it's trendy, it has to look good on you.


          .q What initially attracted you to the fashion industry?
          .a Creativity and glamour.


          .q Which female icon inspires you the most?
          .a I love the way Kate Moss wears clothes. I mean, who doesn't?...


          .q Describe your fashion evolution from teenager to now - what inspired you along the way?
          .a I was always reading magazines and trying to get that look! I kind of dress somewhat similarly from high school now that I think about it, my wardrobe has just gotten increasingly expensive over the years!


          .q Where do you draw your fashion inspiration from?
          .a I'm inspired by my environment, travel, creativity is everywhere.


          .q F&P is all about individuality; if you could choose one word to describe the way you express your individuality, what would it be?
          .a Fun.


          .q Discovering who you are as a young woman can be a tough process; what do you say to young girls out there going through this?
          .a Always feel comfortable whatever you are doing. Comfortable equals confident. And when you feel confident you look good!


          .q If there is a defining moment in your life where you feel you did something that screams your individuality as a woman, what was it?
          .a Dying my hair, green, blue, purple - that was pretty individual! 

          .q What inspired you to collaborate with Fame & Partners?
          .a That brand is so in sync with Nylon style it was a perfect match!

